## 🛠️ **COMPLETE BLYNK SETUP (STEP-BY-STEP)**

---

### 🔹 **Step 1 – Install App**

* Download Blynk IoT from Play Store
* Open the app

---

### 🔹 **Step 2 – Create Account**

* Sign up using email
* Verify email
* Login to dashboard

---

### 🔹 **Step 3 – Create Template**

* Click on “Developer Zone”
* Click “New Template”
* Fill details:

```id="temp1"
Template Name → WiFi Robot  
Hardware → ESP32  
Connection Type → WiFi  
```

👉 Click Create

---

### 🔹 **Step 4 – Add Datastreams (VERY IMPORTANT)**

Go to Datastreams → New Datastream → Virtual Pin

Create the following:

| Name     | Virtual Pin | Type    |
| -------- | ----------- | ------- |
| Forward  | V0          | Integer |
| Backward | V1          | Integer |
| Left     | V2          | Integer |
| Right    | V3          | Integer |

👉 Set: ( because we get only 1 and 0 )

```id="set1"
Min = 0  
Max = 1  
```

---

