* Go to Devices
* Click New Device
* Select From Template
* Choose your template
* Click Create

---

### 🔹 **Step 6 – Get Auth Token**

* Open your device
* Copy Auth Token

👉 This will be used in ESP32 code

---

### 🔹 **Step 7 – Create Mobile Dashboard**

* Open Blynk mobile app
* Select your device
* Click Edit Dashboard

